type: parser
name: kaijo/sshd-logs-rfc5424
description: >
  pfSense-specific SSHD log parser for RFC5424 format (FreeBSD/OpenSSH).
  Extracts authentication events, connection attempts, disconnects, and
  invalid user patterns from pfSense CE/Plus logs.

author: kaijo
license: MIT
version: 0.1.6

labels:
  service: sshd
  platform: pfSense
  log_format: rfc5424

tags:
  - pfSense
  - FreeBSD
  - SSH
  - Logs
  - Parser
